= \frac12\left(\frac{1}{1-2x}\sum_{k=0}^\infty\left(\frac{-x^2}{1-2x}\right)^k + \frac{1}{1+2x}\sum_{k=0}^\infty \left(\frac{-x^2}{1+2x}\right)^k\right)
 = \frac12\left(\frac{1}{1-2x}\frac{1}{1-\frac{-x^2}{1-2x}} + \frac{1}{1+2x}\frac{1}{1-\frac{-x^2}{1+2x}}\right)
